  "text": [
    "Yeah. It\u2019s only a matter",
    "of environment if",
    "I\u2019m a genius.",
    "A genius is",
    "kohlrabi in a turnip in",
    "kale in",
    "cellophane",
    "in the freezer.",
    "In",
    "files they descend on",
    "the white skin and",
    "converge in the corner\u2019s",
    "follicles.",
    "The ants are illuminated.",
    "Basta."
